SAM, hi again.
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Here is a little application that calls the CRYPTOGRAPHIC ICSF API'S.
All the programs are in REXX

You need access to keys and to the ICSF

The programs are in xmit format in member XEXEC
The panels are in xmit format in member XPLIB
The messages are in xmit format in member XMLIB

You only have to start with the REXX PCSF and follow the panels
Nota: you have to put your CKDS and your PKDS in program PCSF
      and all the application works with your files

------------------------------------------------------------------

In addition to this, there are the next programs too

   In order to create asymetric keys, I put several keys RSA in the
   members:
              RSA11024
              RSA1512  ---> see this first
              RSA21024
              RSA31024
              RSA41024
              RSA51024
              RSA61024
              RSA71024
              RSA81024
              RSA91024
   This keys are in assembler format for use with a program that
   put them in the PKDS
   You can use program RSACREA changing the member that use to
   put the key inthe PKDS, and the key label, who is RSAPRU.

 . Other programs

   1   Generate random numbers
       COBOL example: randomc
       ASML example:  randoma

   2   Create symetric keys using API   KEY GENERATE
       The program in COBOL:   DESCRECB
       The program in ASM:     DESCREAS
       With the JCL:           CREASIM

   3   Create symetric keys using RANDOM GENERATOR and IMPORT
       The program in COBOL:   DESRANCB
       The program in ASM:     DESRANAS

   4   Signatures
       5.1    RSADSS1 create the key RSADSS for signatures
              RSADSS2 make a signature from a text and verify it.

You can compile all the assembler programs using the proc ASMCOMP
You can compile all the cobol programs using the proc COBCOMP

DESCREAS.text:
TITLE 'KEY CREATION WITH KEY GENERATE'
*----------------------------------------------------------------------
DESCREAS START 0
         DS    0H
         STM   14,12,12(13)
         BALR  12,0
         USING *,12
         LA    14,SAVE
         ST    13,4(14)
         ST    14,8(13)
         LR    13,14
*-----------------------------------------------
*  CALL KEY GENERATE
*-----------------------------------------------
         CALL  CSNBKGN,(RETCD,RESCD,EXDATAL,EXDATA,                    *
               KEY_FORM,KEY_LEN,KEYTYP1,KEYTYP2,                       *
               KEK_ID1,KEK_ID2,DATA_ID,NULL_ID)
         CLC   RETCD,=F'0'
         BNE   ERROR
*-----------------------------------------------
*  CALL CLEAR KEY RECORD CREATE
*-----------------------------------------------
         CALL  CSNBKRC,(RETCD,RESCD,EXDATAL,EXDATA,KEY_LABEL)
         CLC   RETCD,=F'0'
         BNE   ERROR
*-----------------------------------------------
*  CALL CLEAR KEY RECORD WRITE
*-----------------------------------------------
         CALL  CSNBKRW,(RETCD,RESCD,EXDATAL,EXDATA,DATA_ID,KEY_LABEL)
         CLC   RETCD,=F'0'
         BNE   ERROR
*-----------------------------------------------
RETURN   EQU   *
         L     13,4(13)
         MVC   16(4,13),RETCD
         LM    14,12,12(13)
         BR    14
*-----------------------------------------------------
ERROR    EQU   *
         L     2,RETCD
         L     3,RESCD
         ABEND (2),REASON=(3),DUMP
*-----------------------------------------------------
*  VARIABLES Y CONSTANTES
*-----------------------------------------------------
RETCD    DS    F'0'
RESCD    DS    F'0'
EXDATAL  DC    F'0'
EXDATA   DS    0C
*
KEY_FORM DC    CL4'OP  '
KEY_LEN  DC    CL8'SINGLE  '
KEYTYP1  DC    CL8'DATA    '
KEYTYP2  DC    CL8'        '
DATA_ID  DC    XL64'00'
NULL_ID  DC    XL64'00'
KEK_ID1  DC    XL64'00'
KEK_ID2  DC    XL64'00'
*
KEY_LABEL DC    CL64'ASMKEYCREATE'
*
SAVE     DS    18F
         END

DESCRECB.text:
ID DIVISION.
      *---------------------------------------------------------
      *  DES KEY - KEY GENERATE
      *---------------------------------------------------------
       PROGRAM-ID.    DESCRECB.
       DATE-COMPILED. &SYSDATE.
       AUTHOR.        PERGENTINO.
      *---------------------------------------------------------
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
      *---------------------------------------------------------
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       SOURCE-COMPUTER.  IBM-9021  WITH DEBUGGING MODE.
       OBJECT-COMPUTER.  IBM-9021.

      *---------------------------------------------------------
       DATA DIVISION.
      *---------------------------------------------------------
       FILE SECTION.
      *
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *
      * DEFINE API INPUT/OUTPUT PARAMETERS
      *
       01  API-REC.
           05  RETURN-COD                 PIC 9(8) COMP.
           05  REASON-COD                 PIC 9(8) COMP.
           05  EXIT-DATA-LENGTH           PIC 9(8) COMP.
           05  EXIT-DATA                  PIC X(4).
           05  KEY-FORM                   PIC X(4)
               VALUE 'OP  '.
           05  KEY-LEN                    PIC X(8)
               VALUE 'SINGLE  '.
           05  KEY-TYP1                   PIC X(8)
               VALUE 'DATA    '.
           05  KEY-TYP2                   PIC X(8)
               VALUE '        '.
           05  DATA-ID                    PIC X(64)
               VALUE LOW-VALUES.
           05  NULL-ID                    PIC X(64)
               VALUE LOW-VALUES.
           05  KEY-ID1                    PIC X(64)
               VALUE LOW-VALUES.
           05  KEY-ID2                    PIC X(64)
               VALUE LOW-VALUES.
           05  KEY-LABEL                  PIC X(64)
               VALUE 'COBOLKEYCREATE'.
      *
      *---------------------------------------------------------
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
      *---------------------------------------------------------
       MAIN-RTN.
      *--------- CALL KEY GENERATE ----------------------
           CALL 'CSFKGN' USING  RETURN-COD
                                REASON-COD
                                EXIT-DATA-LENGTH
                                EXIT-DATA
                                KEY-FORM
                                KEY-LEN
                                KEY-TYP1
                                KEY-TYP2
                                KEY-ID1
                                KEY-ID2
                                DATA-ID
                                NULL-ID.
           IF RETURN-COD NOT = 0 THEN
              DISPLAY '*** KEY GENERATE ***'
              DISPLAY '*** RETURN-COD = ' RETURN-COD
              DISPLAY '*** REASON-COD = ' REASON-COD
              MOVE RETURN-COD TO RETURN-CODE
              STOP RUN
           END-IF.
      *--------- CALL RECORD CREATE --------------
           CALL 'CSFKRC' USING  RETURN-COD
                                REASON-COD
                                EXIT-DATA-LENGTH
                                EXIT-DATA
                                KEY-LABEL.
           IF RETURN-COD NOT = 0 THEN
              DISPLAY '*** RECORD CREATE ***'
              DISPLAY '*** RETURN-COD = ' RETURN-COD
              DISPLAY '*** REASON-COD = ' REASON-COD
              MOVE RETURN-COD TO RETURN-CODE
              STOP RUN
           END-IF.
      *--------- CALL RECORD WRITE ---------------
           CALL 'CSFKRW' USING  RETURN-COD
                                REASON-COD
                                EXIT-DATA-LENGTH
                                EXIT-DATA
                                DATA-ID
                                KEY-LABEL.
           IF RETURN-COD NOT = 0 THEN
              DISPLAY '*** RECORD WRITE ***'
              DISPLAY '*** RETURN-COD = ' RETURN-COD
              DISPLAY '*** REASON-COD = ' REASON-COD
              MOVE RETURN-COD TO RETURN-CODE
              STOP RUN
           END-IF.
           DISPLAY '*** KEY COBOLKEYCREATE O.K. ***'
           STOP RUN.

DESRANAS.text:
TITLE 'KEY DES FROM A RANDOM'
*----------------------------------------------------------------------
DESRANAS START 0
         DS    0H
         STM   14,12,12(13)
         BALR  12,0
         USING *,12
         LA    14,SAVE
         ST    13,4(14)
         ST    14,8(13)
         LR    13,14
*----------------------------------------------------------
*  RANDOM GENERATOR -> NUMBER
*----------------------------------------------------------
         CALL  CSNBRNG,(RETCD,RESCD,EXDATAL,EXDATA,FORM,NUMBER)
         CLC   RETCD,=F'0'
         BNE   ERROR
*-----------------------------------------------
*  CALL CLEAR KEY IMPORT   NUMBER-IMPORT AS-KEY_TOKEN
*-----------------------------------------------
         CALL  CSNBCKI,(RETCD,RESCD,EXDATAL,EXDATA,NUMBER,KEY_TOKEN)
         CLC   RETCD,=F'0'
         BNE   ERROR
*-----------------------------------------------
*  CALL CLEAR KEY RECORD CREATE
*-----------------------------------------------
         CALL  CSNBKRC,(RETCD,RESCD,EXDATAL,EXDATA,KEY_LABEL)
         CLC   RETCD,=F'0'
         BNE   ERROR
*-----------------------------------------------
*  CALL CLEAR KEY RECORD WRITE
*-----------------------------------------------
         CALL  CSNBKRW,(RETCD,RESCD,EXDATAL,EXDATA,KEY_TOKEN,KEY_LABEL)
         CLC   RETCD,=F'0'
         BNE   ERROR
*-----------------------------------------------
RETURN   EQU   *
         L     13,4(13)
         MVC   16(4,13),RETCD
         LM    14,12,12(13)
         BR    14
*-----------------------------------------------------
ERROR    EQU   *
         L     2,RETCD
         L     3,RESCD
         ABEND (2),REASON=(3),DUMP
*-----------------------------------------------------
*  VARIABLES Y CONSTANTES
*-----------------------------------------------------
RETCD    DS    F'0'
RESCD    DS    F'0'
EXDATAL  DC    F'0'
EXDATA   DS    0C
*
NUMBER   DS    CL8' '
FORM     DC    CL8'ODD'
*
KEY_TOKEN DS   CL64
*
KEY_LABEL DC    CL64'DESRANAS'
*
SAVE     DS    18F
         END

DESRANCB.text:
ID DIVISION.
      *---------------------------------------------------------
      *  DES KEY WITH RANDOM GENERATOR
      *---------------------------------------------------------
       PROGRAM-ID.    DESRANCB.
       DATE-COMPILED. &SYSDATE.
       AUTHOR.        PERGENTINO.
      *---------------------------------------------------------
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
      *---------------------------------------------------------
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       SOURCE-COMPUTER.  IBM-9021.
       OBJECT-COMPUTER.  IBM-9021.

      *---------------------------------------------------------
       DATA DIVISION.
      *---------------------------------------------------------
       FILE SECTION.
      *
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *
      * DEFINE API INPUT/OUTPUT PARAMETERS
      *
       01  API-REC.
           05  RETURN-COD                 PIC 9(8) COMP.
           05  REASON-COD                 PIC 9(8) COMP.
           05  EXIT-DATA-LENGTH           PIC 9(8) COMP.
           05  EXIT-DATA                  PIC X(4).
           05  NUM-FORM                   PIC X(8)
               VALUE 'RANDOM  '.
           05  NUMERO                     PIC 9(8) COMP.
           05  KEY-TOKEN                  PIC X(64)
               VALUE LOW-VALUES.
           05  KEY-LABEL                  PIC X(64)
               VALUE 'DESRANCB'.
      *
      *---------------------------------------------------------
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
      *---------------------------------------------------------
       MAIN-RTN.
      *--------- CALL GENERADOR DE NUMEROS ALEATORIOS ---
           MOVE 0              TO EXIT-DATA-LENGTH.
           CALL 'CSFRNG' USING  RETURN-COD
                                REASON-COD
                                EXIT-DATA-LENGTH
                                EXIT-DATA
                                NUM-FORM
                                NUMERO.
           IF RETURN-COD NOT = 0 THEN
              DISPLAY '*** GENERADOR NUM. ALEATORIOS ***'
              DISPLAY '*** RETURN-COD = ' RETURN-COD
              DISPLAY '*** REASON-COD = ' REASON-COD
              MOVE RETURN-COD TO RETURN-CODE
              STOP RUN
           END-IF.
      *--------- CALL KEY IMPORT ------------------------
           CALL 'CSFCKI' USING  RETURN-COD
                                REASON-COD
                                EXIT-DATA-LENGTH
                                EXIT-DATA
                                NUMERO
                                KEY-TOKEN.
           IF RETURN-COD NOT = 0 THEN
              DISPLAY '*** KEY IMPORT ***'
              DISPLAY '*** RETURN-COD = ' RETURN-COD
              DISPLAY '*** REASON-COD = ' REASON-COD
              MOVE RETURN-COD TO RETURN-CODE
              STOP RUN
           END-IF.
      *--------- CALL RECORD CREATE --------------
           CALL 'CSFKRC' USING  RETURN-COD
                                REASON-COD
                                EXIT-DATA-LENGTH
                                EXIT-DATA
                                KEY-LABEL.
           IF RETURN-COD NOT = 0 THEN
              DISPLAY '*** RECORD CREATE ***'
              DISPLAY '*** RETURN-COD = ' RETURN-COD
              DISPLAY '*** REASON-COD = ' REASON-COD
              MOVE RETURN-COD TO RETURN-CODE
              STOP RUN
           END-IF.
      *--------- CALL RECORD WRITE ---------------
           CALL 'CSFKRW' USING  RETURN-COD
                                REASON-COD
                                EXIT-DATA-LENGTH
                                EXIT-DATA
                                KEY-TOKEN
                                KEY-LABEL.
           IF RETURN-COD NOT = 0 THEN
              DISPLAY '*** RECORD WRITE ***'
              DISPLAY '*** RETURN-COD = ' RETURN-COD
              DISPLAY '*** REASON-COD = ' REASON-COD
              MOVE RETURN-COD TO RETURN-CODE
              STOP RUN
           END-IF.
           DISPLAY '*** KEY   DESRANCB   O.K. ***'
           STOP RUN.

RANDOMA.text:
TITLE 'RANDOM GENERATION'
*----------------------------------------------------------------------
RANDOMA  START 0
         DS    0H
         STM   14,12,12(13)
         BALR  12,0
         USING *,12
         LA    14,SAVE
         ST    13,4(14)
         ST    14,8(13)
         LR    13,14
*-----------------------------------------------
*  CALL RANDOM GENERATOR
*-----------------------------------------------
         CALL  CSFRNG,(RETCD,RESCD,EXDATAL,EXDATA,                     *
               FORM,                                                   *
               NUMBER)
         CLC   RETCD,=F'0'
         BNE   BACK
         CLC   RESCD,=F'0'
         BNE   BACK
         MVC   WTOX+14(8),NUMBER
WTOX     WTO   'NUM -> PERGEN <-',ROUTCDE=11
*-----------------------------------------------
RETURN   EQU   *
         L     13,4(13)
         MVC   16(4,13),RETCD
         LM    14,12,12(13)
         BR    14
*-----------------------------------------------------
*  CONVERT RETURN/REASON CODES FROM BINARY TO EBCDIC
*-----------------------------------------------------
BACK     DS    0F
         L     5,RETCD
         L     6,RESCD
         CVD   5,BCD1
         CVD   6,BCD2
         UNPK  ORETCD,BCD1
         UNPK  ORESCD,BCD2
         OI    ORETCD+7,X'F0'
         OI    ORESCD+7,X'F0'
*
         MVC   ERROUT+21(4),ORETCD+4
         MVC   ERROUT+41(4),ORESCD+4
ERROUT   WTO   'ERROR CODE = XXXX, REASON CODE = XXXX',ROUTCDE=11
         B     RETURN
*-----------------------------------------------------
BCD1     DS    D
BCD2     DS    D
ORETCD   DS    CL8'0'
ORESCD   DS    CL8'0'
*
RETCD    DS    F'0'
RESCD    DS    F'0'
EXDATAL  DC    F'0'
EXDATA   DS    0C
NUMBER   DS    CL8' '
FORM     DC    CL8'RANDOM'
*FORM     DC    CL8'ODD'
*FORM     DC    CL8'EVEN'
SAVE     DS    18F
         END   RANDOMA

RANDOMC.text:
ID DIVISION.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------
      *  OBTENCION DE NUMEROS ALEATORIOS
      *-----------------------------------------------------------
       PROGRAM-ID.    RANDOMC.
       DATE-COMPILED. &SYSDATE.
       AUTHOR.        PERGEN.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       SOURCE-COMPUTER.  IBM-9021  WITH DEBUGGING MODE.
       OBJECT-COMPUTER.  IBM-9021.

      *-----------------------------------------------------------
       DATA DIVISION.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------
       FILE SECTION.
      *
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  NUMERO-ED                      PIC +++++++++++++++9.
      *
      * DEFINE SAPI INPUT/OUTPUT PARAMETERS
      *
       01  SAPI-REC.
           05  RETURN-CODE-S              PIC 9(8) COMP.
           05  REASON-CODE-S              PIC 9(8) COMP.
           05  EXIT-DATA-LENGTH-S         PIC 9(8) COMP.
           05  EXIT-DATA-S                PIC X(4).
           05  NUM-FORM-S                 PIC X(8)
               VALUE 'RANDOM  '.
           05  NUMERO-S                   PIC 9(8) COMP.
      *
      *-----------------------------------------------------------
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------
       MAIN-RTN.
      *--------- CALL NUMEROS ALEATORIOS ----------
           MOVE 0              TO EXIT-DATA-LENGTH-S.
           CALL 'CSFRNG' USING  RETURN-CODE-S
                                REASON-CODE-S
                                EXIT-DATA-LENGTH-S
                                EXIT-DATA-S
                                NUM-FORM-S
                                NUMERO-S.
           IF RETURN-CODE-S NOT = 0 OR
              REASON-CODE-S NOT = 0 THEN
              DISPLAY '*** KEY GENERATE ***'
              DISPLAY '*** RETURN-CODE = ' RETURN-CODE-S
              DISPLAY '*** REASON-CODE = ' REASON-CODE-S
              MOVE RETURN-CODE-S TO RETURN-CODE
           ELSE
              MOVE NUMERO-S TO NUMERO-ED
              DISPLAY '* NUM * ' NUMERO-ED
           END-IF.
           STOP RUN.

RSADSS1.text:
TITLE 'CREACION Y ESCRITURA DE CLAVE EN EL PKDS PARA FIRMA'
*----------------------------------------------------------------------
         PRINT NOGEN
         YREGS
RSADSS1  CSECT
         STM   14,12,12(13)
         BALR  10,0
         USING *,10,11,12
         CNOP  0,4
         B     *+8
         DC    A(SAVEAR)
         L     15,*-4
         ST    13,4(15)
         ST    15,8(13)
         LR    13,15
*----------------------------------------------------------------------
* CALL PKA KEY TOKEN BUILD
*----------------------------------------------------------------------
BUILD    CALL  CSNDPKB,(RETCD,RESCD,EXDATAL,EXDATA,RULECN,             *
               RULEARR,KEYVSL,KEYVSEST,KEYPVLE,LABEL,FIL1,FIL1S,       *
               FIL2,FIL2S,FIL3,FIL3S,FIL4,FIL4S,FIL5,FIL5S,            *
               KEYTOKL,KEYTOKEN)
         CLC   RETCD,=F'0'
         BNE   ERROR
         MVC   WTO1+10(100),KEYTOKEN
WTO1     WTO   '->                                                     *
                                                              <-',     *
               ROUTCDE=11
         MVC   WTO2+10(100),KEYTOKL
WTO2     WTO   '->                                                     *
                                                              <-',     *
               ROUTCDE=11
         PRINT GEN
*----------------------------------------------------------------------
* IMPORT CLEAR RSA PRIVATE EXTERNAL KEY
*----------------------------------------------------------------------
IMPORT   CALL  CSNDPKI,(RETCD,RESCD,EXDATAL,EXDATA,RULEICN,            *
               RULEIAR,KEYTOKL,KEYTOKEN,DUMY_KEK,                      *
               INTPKAL,INTPKA)
         CLC   RETCD,=F'0'
         BNE   ERROR
         WTO   '->IMPORTED<-',ROUTCDE=11
*--------------------------------------------------------------------
*  RECORD CREATE
*--------------------------------------------------------------------
CREATE   CALL  CSNDKRC,(RETCD,RESCD,EXDATAL2,EXDATA2,                  *
               RULEIC,RULEI,LABEL,INTPKAL,INTPKA)
         CLC   RETCD,=F'0'
         BNE   ERROR
         WTO   '->CREATED<-',ROUTCDE=11
*----------------------------------------------------------------------
FIN      L     13,4(13)
         RETURN (14,12),RC=0
ERROR    EQU   *
         L     R2,RETCD
         L     R3,RESCD
         ABEND (R2),REASON=(R3),DUMP
*----------------------------------------------------------------------
SAVEAR   DS    18F            SAVEAREA
RETCD    DS    F
RESCD    DS    F
EXDATAL  DC    F'10'
EXDATA   DC    CL8'        ',X'0000'
EXDATAL2 DC    F'0'
EXDATA2  DS    0C
*---CSNDPKB------------------------------------------------------------
RULEARR  DC    CL16'RSA-PRIVKEY-MGMT'
RULECN   DC    F'2'
*RULEARR  DC    CL8'RSA-PRIV'
*RULECN   DC    F'1'
KEYVSL   DC    F'139'
KEYVSEST DS    0CL139
         DC    X'0200' MODULUS LENGTH IN BITS                X'200'=512
         DC    X'0040' MODULUS FIELD LENGTH IN BYTES  XXX -> X'040'=64
         DC    X'0003' PUB EXP FIELD LENGTH IN BYTES  YYY -> X'003'=3
         DC    X'0040' PRIV EXP FIELD LENGTH IN BYTES ZZZ -> X'040'=64
         DC    X'800000000000000001AE28DA4606D885' \
         DC    X'EB7E0340D6BAAC51991C0CD0EAE835AF' | 008 XXX=64
         DC    X'D9CFF3CD7E7EA74141DADD24A6331BED' | MODULUS N
         DC    X'F41A6626522CCF15767D167D01A16F97' /
         DC    X'010001'     RSA PUBLIC EXP          008+XXX YYY=3
         DC    X'0252BDAD4252BDAD425A8C6045D41AFA' \
         DC    X'F746BEBD5F085D574FCD9C07F0B38C2C' | 008+XXX+YYY
         DC    X'45017C2A1AB919ED2551350A76606BFA' |      ZZZ=64
         DC    X'6AF2F1609A00A0A48DD719A55E9CA801' / RSA SECRET EXP D
KEYPVLE  DC    F'64'
FIL1     DC    F'0'
FIL1S    DC    C' '
FIL2     DC    F'0'
FIL2S    DC    C' '
FIL3     DC    F'0'
FIL3S    DC    C' '
FIL4     DC    F'0'
FIL4S    DC    C' '
FIL5     DC    F'0'
FIL5S    DC    C' '
*---CSNDPKB CSNDKRC----------------------------------------------------
KEYTOKEN DC    1024X'00'
KEYTOKL  DC    F'1024'
LABEL    DC    CL64'RSADSS'
*---CSNDPKI------------------------------------------------------------
RULEIAR  DC    CL8' '
RULEICN  DC    F'0'
DUMY_KEK DS    CL64
INTPKAL  DC    F'1024'
INTPKA   DS    CL1024
*---CSNDKRC------------------------------------------------------------
RULEIC    DC   F'0'
RULEI     DC   C' '
*----------------------------------------------------------------------
         LTORG
         END

RSADSS2.text:
TITLE 'DSS Y VERIFICACION'
*----------------------------------------------------------------------
         PRINT NOGEN
         YREGS
RSADSS2  CSECT
         STM   14,12,12(13)
         BALR  10,0
         USING *,10,11,12
         CNOP  0,4
         B     *+8
         DC    A(SAVEAR)
         L     15,*-4
         ST    13,4(15)
         ST    15,8(13)
         LR    13,15
*----------------------------------------------------------------------
*  CALL ONE-WAY HASH TO GET SHA-1
*----------------------------------------------------------------------
         CALL  CSNBOWH,(RETCD,RESCD,EXDATAL,EXDATA,                    *
               RULEACO,RULEAO,                                         *
               TEXTL,TEXT,                                             *
               CVL,CV,HASHL,HASH)
         CLC   RETCD,=F'0'
         BNE   ERROR
         MVC   WT1+14(L'HASH),HASH
WT1      WTO   'HASH->                    <-',ROUTCDE=11
*----------------------------------------------------------------------
* DIGITAL SIGNATURE GENERATE
*----------------------------------------------------------------------
DSSG     CALL  CSNDDSG,(RETCD,RESCD,EXDATAL,EXDATA,RULEDCN,            *
               RULEDAR,INTPKAL,INTPKA,HASHL,HASH,SIGL,SIGBL,SIG)
         CLC   RETCD,=F'0'
         BNE   ERROR
         MVC   WTO5+10(100),SIG
WTO5     WTO   'KT ->                                                  *
                                                                 <-',  *
               ROUTCDE=11
*----------------------------------------------------------------------
* DIGITAL SIGNATURE VERIFY
*----------------------------------------------------------------------
DSSV     CALL  CSNDDSV,(RETCD,RESCD,EXDATAL,EXDATA,RULEDCN,            *
               RULEDAR,INTPKAL,INTPKA,HASHL,HASH,SIGL,SIG)
         CLC   RETCD,=F'0'
         BNE   ERROR
         WTO   'VERIFY -> CORRECT <-',ROUTCDE=11
*----------------------------------------------------------------------
FIN      L     13,4(13)
         RETURN (14,12),RC=0
ERROR    EQU   *
         L     R2,RETCD
         L     R3,RESCD
         ABEND (R2),REASON=(R3),DUMP
*----------------------------------------------------------------------
SAVEAR   DS    18F            SAVEAREA
RETCD    DS    F
RESCD    DS    F
EXDATAL  DC    F'10'
EXDATA   DC    CL8'        ',X'0000'
*---CSNBOWH------------------------------------------------------------
RULEACO  DC    F'2'
RULEAO   DC    CL16'SHA-1   ONLY    '
TEXTL    DC    F'64'
TEXT     DC    CL64'there''s only 10 types of people in the world; thos*
               e that understand binary and those that don''t '
CVL      DC    F'128'
CV       DS    CL128
HASHL    DC    F'20'
HASH     DS    CL20
*---CSNDDSG------------------------------------------------------------
INTPKAL  DC    F'64'
INTPKA   DC    CL64'RSADSS'
RULEDAR  DC    CL8'ISO-9796'
RULEDCN  DC    F'1'
SIGL     DC    F'128'
SIGBL    DS    F'0'
SIG      DS    CL128
*----------------------------------------------------------------------
         LTORG
         END
